title: Nahubi's Will
author: Endergun
pages:
#- This is a final account and memo of me, Nahubi. Snitches have been recording me killing chickens and breaking blocks. This is also a will, should I be pearled and not released/rescued, or, if I am released/rescued, the people at the end can have my stuff 
#- but only until I am released. They do not have to pay for lost items.


#- 